(310, 311, 'About a conjecture regarding plurisubharmonic functions', '[{\"title\":\"A. B\\u00ebrd\\u00ebllima\",\"href\":\"\\/php\\/person.phtml?option_lang=rus&personid=115491\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"<i>Department of Computer Engineering, Faculty of Architecture and Engineering, Epoka University, Albania<\\/i>\",\"href\":\"\\/php\\/organisation.phtml?option_lang=rus&orgid=10627\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"PDF \\u0444\\u0430\\u0439\\u043b\",\"href\":\"\\/php\\/getFT.phtml?jrnid=ufa&paperid=311&what=fullt&option_lang=rus\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"PDF \\u0444\\u0430\\u0439\\u043b\",\"href\":\"\\/php\\/getRefFromDB.phtml?jrnid=ufa&paperid=311&output=pdf&option_lang=rus\"},{\"title\":\"HTML \\u0444\\u0430\\u0439\\u043b\",\"href\":\"\\/php\\/getRefFromDB.phtml?jrnid=ufa&paperid=311&output=htm&option_lang=rus\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"PDF \\u0444\\u0430\\u0439\\u043b\",\"href\":\"\\/php\\/getFT.phtml?jrnid=ufa&paperid=311&what=fullt&option_lang=rus\"}]', '[]', ' In this work we present Khabibullin\'s conjecture in its different equivalent forms. Applying the concept of the integral operator, we transform the original conjecture into a new form which proves to be helpful in studying it by means of the Laplace transform. Using Laplace transform of integral inequalities, we are able to show the uniqueness of a solution that satisfies both inequalities with identity. Furthermore we provide a new proof of Khabibullin\'s theorem by methods of the Laplace transform and contour integration from complex analysis. However, this method of transform fails to prove the conjecture and a brief reasoning is provided. ', 'Khabibullin\'s hypothesis, integral inequalities, plurisubharmonic function, Laplace transform, complex analysis, contour integration, sharp estimate.', '', '[\"311_481.pdf\"]', '[\"311_118.pdf\",\"311_374.html\"]', '31.12.2020'),
